<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢٤٦١ - عَنِ ابْنِ عُيَيْنَةَ، عَنْ رَجُلٍ،<span class="c5"> مِنْهُمْ قَالَ:</span> رَأَى حُذَيْفَةُ رَجُلًا فِي الصَّفَّ الْأَوَّلِ فَأَخَّرَهُ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَسْتَ مِنْهُمْ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>